    "Federated learning critical issues such as data privacy, model generalization, scalability, and inherent biases within AI models.",
    "By allowing multiple institutions to collaboratively train models while keeping their data localized, federated learning not only complies with strict data privacy laws but also enhances the diversity and efficacy of medical AI applications.",
